suncertify.ui.listeners

Class ClientOkButtonListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • suncertify.ui.listeners.AbstractOKButtonListener
      • suncertify.ui.listeners.ClientOkButtonListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.event.ActionListener, java.util.EventListener

    public class ClientOkButtonListener
extends AbstractOKButtonListener
    ClientOkButtonListener extends the abstract class OKButtonListener and is responsible for implementing the relevant methods in this class, such as validating configuration data entered by the user, saving config data to disk, and returning the correct business service for running in client mode. The business service in this case is a remote service and is obtained by querying the RMI Registry with the host details entered by the user.

    Kieran O'Brien
